' plan-58-A rule 8 — the latent hole this sub-plan closes (§2.3).
'
' BEFORE plan-58 this file COMPILED. A LINK wrapper's MFBASIC return type was
' almost entirely unvalidated against its ABI return, `emit_return_passthrough`
' has no List-building arm, so RESULT_VALUE_REGISTER received a raw scalar that
' the caller then dereferenced as a collection block. Garbage, no diagnostic.
' Only a CBuffer can produce a byte list.
LINK "demo" AS demoLink
  FUNC bogus(n AS Integer) AS List OF Byte
    SYMBOL "demo_read"
    ABI (n CInt64) AS r CInt64
    RETURN r
  END FUNC
END LINK
